s\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"the details\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A handful of journalists, including AFP, were able to attend just a few minutes of a rehearsal this month.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999982612735, \"rank\": 1.6755138663032668e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A handful\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"just a few minutes\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"a rehearsal\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neon lights and disco balls contrasted with the industrial chaos of the decrepit but immense hangar.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Neon lights and disco balls\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"the industrial chaos\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the decrepit but immense hangar\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such a huge space was necessary because - for the first time in Olympics history - the opening ceremony is not taking place in a stadium.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Such a huge space\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics history\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 915}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it will stretch across seven kilometres of the River Seine with more than 3,000 dancers p